des:
Listen to weekly running tips from World-Ranked and All-American track athlete, Tina Klein.
Tina Klein, is a certified run coach, and current world ranked and All-American track athlete. Tina created Balanced Running with passion to bring the benefits of a balanced life through running to as many people as possible. For more running resources, out Tina Klein's website at www.balancedrunningllc.com
You can just say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing". You can say "Alexa, stop" to exit anytime.
